{"tha-ap336:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap336:0.2":"Gandhodakavagga ","tha-ap336:0.3":"Ekadussadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap336:1.1":"“Nagare hamsavatiya, ","tha-ap336:1.2":"ahosim tinaharako; ","tha-ap336:1.3":"Tinaharena jivami, ","tha-ap336:1.4":"tena posemi darake. ","tha-ap336:2.1":"Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap336:2.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","tha-ap336:2.3":"Tamandhakaram nasetva, ","tha-ap336:2.4":"uppajji lokanayako. ","tha-ap336:3.1":"Sake ghare nisiditva, ","tha-ap336:3.2":"evam cintesaham tada; ","tha-ap336:3.3":"‘Buddho loke samuppanno, ","tha-ap336:3.4":"deyyadhammo ca natthi me. ","tha-ap336:4.1":"Idam me satakam ekam, ","tha-ap336:4.2":"natthi me koci dayako; ","tha-ap336:4.3":"Dukkho nirayasamphasso, ","tha-ap336:4.4":"ropayissami dakkhinam’. ","tha-ap336:5.1":"Evaham cintayitvana, ","tha-ap336:5.2":"sakam cittam pasadayim; ","tha-ap336:5.3":"Ekam dussam gahetvana, ","tha-ap336:5.4":"buddhasetthassadasaham. ","tha-ap336:6.1":"Ekam dussam daditvana, ","tha-ap336:6.2":"ukkutthim sampavattayim; ","tha-ap336:6.3":"Yadi buddho tuvam vira, ","tha-ap336:6.4":"tarehi mam mahamuni. ","tha-ap336:7.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap336:7.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap336:7.3":"Mama danam pakittento, ","tha-ap336:7.4":"aka me anumodanam. ","tha-ap336:8.1":"‘Imina ekadussena, ","tha-ap336:8.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap336:8.3":"Kappasatasahassani, ","tha-ap336:8.4":"vinipatam na gacchati. ","tha-ap336:9.1":"Chattimsakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap336:9.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap336:9.3":"Tettimsakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap336:9.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap336:9.5":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap336:9.6":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap336:10.1":"Devaloke manusse va, ","tha-ap336:10.2":"samsaranto tuvam bhave; ","tha-ap336:10.3":"Rupava gunasampanno, ","tha-ap336:10.4":"anavakkantadehava; ","tha-ap336:10.5":"Akkhobham amitam dussam, ","tha-ap336:10.6":"labhissati yadicchakam’. ","tha-ap336:11.1":"Idam vatvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap336:11.2":"jalajuttamanamako; ","tha-ap336:11.3":"Nabham abbhuggami dhiro, ","tha-ap336:11.4":"hamsarajava ambare. ","tha-ap336:12.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap336:12.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap336:12.3":"Bhoge me unata natthi, ","tha-ap336:12.4":"ekadussassidam phalam. ","tha-ap336:13.1":"Paduddhare paduddhare, ","tha-ap336:13.2":"dussam nibbattate mamam; ","tha-ap336:13.3":"Hettha dussamhi titthami, ","tha-ap336:13.4":"upari chadanam mama. ","tha-ap336:14.1":"Cakkavalamupadaya, ","tha-ap336:14.2":"sakananam sapabbatam; ","tha-ap336:14.3":"Icchamano caham ajja, ","tha-ap336:14.4":"dussehi chadayeyyaham. ","tha-ap336:15.1":"Teneva ekadussena, ","tha-ap336:15.2":"samsaranto bhavabhave; ","tha-ap336:15.3":"Suvannavanno hutvana, ","tha-ap336:15.4":"samsarami bhavabhave. ","tha-ap336:16.1":"Vipakam ekadussassa, ","tha-ap336:16.2":"najjhagam katthacikkhayam; ","tha-ap336:16.3":"Ayam me antima jati, ","tha-ap336:16.4":"vipaccati idhapi me. ","tha-ap336:17.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap336:17.2":"yam dussamadadim tada; ","tha-ap336:17.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap336:17.4":"ekadussassidam phalam. ","tha-ap336:18.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap336:18.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap336:18.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap336:18.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap336:19.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap336:19.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap336:19.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap336:20.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekadussadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap336:21.1":"Ekadussadayakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}